          "reviewBody": "I had the privilege of studying at Emma Thompson School since  nursery and it has been an extraordinary journey that has shaped me into the person I am today. Today I am working as a successfully. From the moment I stepped into the school as a young child to the day I graduated, every experience has been invaluable. Thanks ETS...",
