            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I would have not given it even a one star if it was not compulsory. if you are seeking to waste your money & time this school might be the best of the options available. The fees here is around 49,095 per annum. Which is unreasonably high since they do not provide any servies even after taking this much of an amount . The staff members have no displine & manners they usually argue with parents + also disrepect them\nIf for any reason you are wanting to meet the principal they'll say \"you cannot meet her for which ever reason you are wanting to \" . And especially never ask them for any fees reduction or time delay for paying the fees  (even if you facing financial unstability) cause they will just shout at you and send you back !",
